                                        </ul>
                                    </li>
                                    <li style="margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 6pt; line-height: 8.2pt;">
                                        <span style="font-weight: 800; display: block; font-size: 7.2pt; line-height: 8pt; margin-bottom: 5px;">15. Are there any fees which are charges in the premium paid for the DTA Insurance?</span>
                                        As an Insurance agent licensed by the FSC to act on behalf of MUA Life and NICL Ltd, the bank will earn a commission which is included in the gross premium paid by the customer. The premium is also inclusive of other charges namely the FSC fees and other taxes.
                                        <span style="font-weight: 800; display: block;">Note:</span>
