                                            <li>The premium for single payment is cheapest compared to monthly and annual installments. </li>
                                            <li>The commission earned is disclosed in the product documentation (signed application form) of the preferred Insurance company </li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <span style="font-weight: 800; display: block;">Note:</span>
