                                            <li>2. Please note that the premiums from other insurance providers may be higher or lower than what is being offered via Absa Bank (Mauritius) Ltd.</li>
                                            <li>3. The list of insurance service providers may change, subject to future negotiation.</li>
                                            <li>4. The purchase of an Insurance policy is a separate product and specifically contemplated by the customer.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </li>
